g U.S. manufacturing  ...    The Oberon facility in California with 679 MWp of solar and 1 GWh of storage came online in 2023 below budget and ahead  ...    deployment at speed and scale regardless of market volatility. We fast-tracked the procurement and installation of a  ...    deploying large-scale energy infrastructure. Oberon is now part of IPX Power’s portfolio. ## Insights from Sheldon Kimber.\n\n22 Dec 2025\n\nIt Goes to 11… Intersect’s Next Phase\n\n15 Apr 2025 Hybrid Gas and Renewable Solutions: Not Your Grandparents’ Baseload Power\n\n05 Sep 2024 Decarbonization, Digitalization, and Electrification: As Megatrends Collide, AI Data Center Demand Is a Preview of What’s to Come 09 Aug 2023\n\nThe Future of the Grid"
